question:
District category contains Industrial District, College Town, and Historic Neighborhood.
Supermarkets category contains Aldi, Loblaws, and Fresh Thyme Market.
Product category contains Canned Mushrooms, Half-and-half, and Canned Pineapple.
Ingredient category contains Grits, Nuts, and Hoisin Sauce.
The number of each Aldi 's Half-and-half equals 16.
The number of each College Town 's Fresh Thyme Market equals each Half-and-half 's Ingredient.
The number of each Loblaws 's Canned Mushrooms equals 13 more than each Aldi 's Canned Pineapple.
The number of each Canned Pineapple 's Nuts equals 21.
The number of each Historic Neighborhood 's Aldi equals 14 times the difference of each Loblaws 's Canned Pineapple and each Canned Mushrooms 's Hoisin Sauce.
The number of each Loblaws 's Canned Pineapple equals 9.
The number of each Canned Mushrooms 's Hoisin Sauce equals 1.
The number of each Industrial District 's Fresh Thyme Market equals 2.
The number of each Industrial District 's Aldi equals 1 times each Canned Mushrooms 's Nuts.
The number of each Industrial District 's Loblaws equals 11 times each Canned Pineapple 's Nuts.
The number of each Canned Mushrooms 's Nuts equals each Half-and-half 's Hoisin Sauce.
The number of each College Town 's Loblaws equals the sum of each Historic Neighborhood 's Aldi, each Aldi 's Canned Mushrooms, each Loblaws 's Canned Pineapple, and each Canned Mushrooms 's Hoisin Sauce.
The number of each Aldi 's Canned Mushrooms equals the sum of each Loblaws 's Canned Pineapple, each Historic Neighborhood 's Aldi, and each Canned Mushrooms 's Hoisin Sauce.
The number of each Canned Mushrooms 's Grits equals 20.
The number of each Half-and-half 's Hoisin Sauce equals each Industrial District 's Loblaws.
The number of each Aldi 's Canned Pineapple equals 12.
The number of each Historic Neighborhood 's Fresh Thyme Market equals 10 more than each Canned Mushrooms 's Nuts.
The number of each Fresh Thyme Market 's Canned Mushrooms equals 4 more than the difference of each Loblaws 's Canned Pineapple and each Aldi 's Canned Mushrooms.
How many Fresh Thyme Market does Historic Neighborhood have?
solution:
Define each Canned Pineapple 's Nuts as J; So J = 21.
Define each Industrial District 's Loblaws as p; So p = 11 * J = 11 * 21 = 1.
Define each Half-and-half 's Hoisin Sauce as q; So q = p = 1.
Define each Canned Mushrooms 's Nuts as x; So x = q = 1.
Define each Historic Neighborhood 's Fresh Thyme Market as y; So y = 10 + x = 10 + 1 = 11.
